<task id="create-transformation-scenario">
  <title>Duplicating a Transformation Scenario</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>Transformation Scenario<indexterm>new transformation scenario<indexterm>create a
              transformation scenario</indexterm></indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <context>Use the following procedure to duplicate a transformation scenario.</context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Go to menu <menucascade>
            <uicontrol product="editor author developer"> Document</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol product="editor author developer"> Transformation</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol product="editorEclipse authorEclipse developerEclipse"> XML</uicontrol>
            <uicontrol>Configure Transformation Scenario (<shortcut
                conref="../topics/oxygen-shortcuts-list.dita#oxygen-shortcuts-list/shortcut_ctrl_shift_c"
                product="editor author developer"/>
              <shortcut
                conref="../topics/oxygen-shortcuts-list.dita#oxygen-shortcuts-list/alt_shift_tc_shortcut"
                product="authorEclipse developerEclipse editorEclipse"/></uicontrol>
          </menucascade>) to open the <uicontrol>Configure Transformation</uicontrol> dialog.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Duplicate Scenario</uicontrol> button of the dialog to create a
          copy of the current scenario.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Name</uicontrol> field and type a new name.</cmd>
        <substeps>
          <substep>
            <cmd>You can choose to save the scenarios at project level by setting the
                <uicontrol>Project Scenarios</uicontrol> setting.</cmd>
          </substep>
        </substeps>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click <uicontrol>OK</uicontrol> or <uicontrol>Transform Now </uicontrol> to save the
          scenario.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
  <related-links product="author editor developer">
    <link href="../topics/preferences-sharing.dita#preferences-sharing"/>
  </related-links>
</task>